metadata.name: // ME //
metadata.description:
// ME // is my most personal piece yet. It illustrates all the things that were and are said to me by some bullies throughout my life. Although they made my life truly miserable, I forgive them. For it was due to them I became who I am today, and am able to pour my heart out in my artworks.

I hope you as a human can connect to this piece too at some level.
